#: Game.Levels.SetWorld.L09_Boss
msgid "# Boss: Putting It All Together\n"
"\n"
"Time to combine everything. You are given an abstract predicate §0\n"
"on natural numbers, with two hypotheses:\n"
"\n"
"- §1 — every even number satisfies §2\n"
"- §3 — every number satisfying §4 is even\n"
"\n"
"Together these say: §5 holds for exactly the even numbers.\n"
"\n"
"You must prove two things:\n"
"1. §6 — 4 is in the p-set (because 4 is even)\n"
"2. §7 — 3 is NOT in the p-set (because 3 is odd)\n"
"\n"
"This combines:\n"
"- Membership via hypothesis (Levels 1–2, 4): use §8 then\n"
"  provide a witness for §9\n"
"- Non-membership via contradiction (Levels 3, 5): assume §10,\n"
"  derive §11 from §12, destructure the existential with\n"
"  §13, then reach an arithmetic contradiction\n"
"\n"
"Start with §14 to split the conjunction."
msgstr ""

