#: Game.Levels.SetWorld.L06_EmptySet
msgid "# The Empty Set\n"
"\n"
"The **empty set** §0 is the set with no elements.\n"
"Its predicate is §1 — it returns §2 for every input.\n"
"\n"
"So §3 reduces to §4. Since §5 has no proof,\n"
"nothing can ever be a member of §6.\n"
"\n"
"Your task is to prove that NO natural number belongs to §7. The\n"
"statement is §8.\n"
"\n"
"The proof has two layers:\n"
"1. §9 — introduce the universally quantified §10\n"
"2. §11 — since §12 is §13 which is §14,\n"
"   introduce the hypothesis §15\n"
"3. Now §16 has type §17 (since §18 reduces to §19),\n"
"   and the goal is §20, so §21 finishes.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove the statement step by step."
msgstr ""

