msgid "# Non-Membership: §0 means §1\n"
"\n"
"Just as §2 means the predicate §3 holds at §4, non-membership\n"
"§5 means the predicate does NOT hold. Formally:\n"
"\n"
"§6\n"
"\n"
"So §7 unfolds to §8, which is §9.\n"
"\n"
"To prove a negation §10, you assume §11 and derive a contradiction.\n"
"The tactic §12 turns a goal §13 into a goal §14 with\n"
